cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "aridkpi: climate-resilience KPIs for residential buildings in arid South American climates"
abstract: >-
  Python package implementing the 5 core KPIs of the IEA EBC Annex 80
  framework, extended for arid and semi-arid climates of South America
  (BWk/BSk Köppen-Geiger). Implements Indoor Overheating Degree (IOD),
  Climate Change Overheating Resistivity (CCOR), Unmet Degree Hours
  during outage (UDH), energy sensitivity (delta E / delta T) and
  maximum indoor thermal change rate (dT/dt max).
